entries.femaleVariant: Who else wants a shot at Holt? I can't hear you!
Any more Second Amendment fans in the house? Huh?
To Gunner!
Listen up! Gunner wants you all to have a good time. A good fuckin' time!
So we got a prize for the winner!
Yeeeaahh! Woo-hooooo!
Well? Who else wants to try their luck?
The hell you want?
What'd you say to me?
What'd you say?
Said to fuck off. But I see you didn't catch my drift. Yo, Joe!
Huh?
C'mere. We got a smartass punk here, can't seem to find her way out.
entries.maleVariant: C'mere. We got a smartass punk here, can't seem to find his way out.

entries.femaleVariant: Yeah, we all wanna good laugh, Walker.
I'm in.
What are the rules?
And the rules of the game?
Now, this ain't your average shootin' match. You gotta have a good eye... but an even stronger head.
'Cause we all drink a round before each shot. To Gunner, the new boss in town.
Like the sound of that. Anything else I should know?
Four stations. You shoot at the targets with Holt's face in the time limit. The more bootlickers you pop, the better.
High score so far belongs to Walker – forty three points. You beat him... prize is yours.
Nah, not for me.
Let's shoot the shit outta Holt.
Take this revolver. Use it if you want your shots to count. We're testin' skill, not tech here.
[Drink]
Aackhh...
Twelve seconds! Go!
Stop! Time's up! Next station!
Hey, hey! Vodka first! Then you blast Holt a new one!
[Drink]
Ughh... The hell's this? Rubbing alcohol?
Who cares! Shoot! You got twelve seconds!
Aaaand... Stop! Next station!
Down the hatch! To Gunner!
[Drink]
Ooof...
You got twelve seconds! Go, go, go!
Stop! Last station!
One more round! Drink!
[Drink]
Ugh... So warm...
What else would it be in this heat? Shoot! Twelve seconds!
Time's up! That's it! Go check your stats!
Now let's see...
Last place. Choom, even Keebler did better.
Fourth place... out of five. Congrats, you beat Keebler.
Third place. Middle of the road.
Second place. Not bad, not bad.
First place. By a landslide. Here... Won it fair and square.
Hahahaha!
And for the winner... With Gunner's congratulations.
Woo-hooo! N-U-S-A! N-U-S-A!
And now – let's drink! 6th Street! 6th Street!
Hahahahah!
Not bad... For a no-name little punk.
Would ya look at that. The punk is good for something.
The hell?! Not fuckin' possible!
Not gonna lie, I'm impressed.
Y'know – 6th Street could use a few more shooters like you. I'm sure Gunner'd like to meet ya. Take you under his wing, probably.
Hey! Hey, you! Where do I know you from, huh?
Wait, I know! I know where I saw you before! You were shooting at us!
Look, I dunno why you're here or what you want. But I know what you're gonna get! Zero her!
entries.maleVariant: Look, I dunno why you're here or what you want. But I know what you're gonna get! Zero him!

entries.femaleVariant: I'm tellin' ya, man... The breeze... Whoosh! Th-threw it all off...
'Ey! But, but I said, my finger slipped...
You had your chance, Rudy.
No fuckin' fair...
I'ma... I'ma throw up...
That a trick question? This is a party, right?
Invitation only. For those who bleed red, white and blue. So fuck off.
Chill. Just wanna have some fun.
Whatever. See you.
Chill. Just wanted to have a good time. Drink a beer, smoke.
Whatever. I'm out.
What, you deaf? Fuckin' scram!
Sorry. I'll be off.
This look like a fuckin' neighborhood picnic to you?
Choom, you are a little tense. Something wrong? Problems at home?
entries.maleVariant: Choom, you're a little tense. Something wrong? Problems at home?

entries.femaleVariant: OK, here's what's gonna happen. You say "I'm sorry," then you fuckin' delta.
Or else I delta you myself. Right to the bottom of the Del Coronado.
Or else what?
[Draw weapon]
My bad.
Very good. Now get out before I change my mind.
Sorry, really sorry...
But I'm gonna have to shut this party down.
Oh, you're a jokester, huh? You lookin' for a good laugh?
Such a nice day, everyone havin' a good time. Like a little 4th of July. Be a shame to tell Gunner someone fucked it up, y'know?
Yeah, I know. Fine.
That's my choom. Go, drink, enjoy yourself. Celebrate that decent score of yours.
Just as I thought. You looked to me like a show-off. Let's see what ya got.
Because...?
Enough talkin'. Let's shoot.
Go ahead to the first station. We'll start whenever you're ready. Break a leg.
Gunner can jump off a megabuilding.
Thanks, but no thanks.
Gunner can go jump off 'Saka Tower.
You come on our turf. Crash our party. Drink our booze. And now you wanna insult the host?
This I don't like. How 'bout you, Walker?
Me neither. Not one fuckin' bit.
I'm flattered, really, but... I gotta say no. Not for me.
entries.maleVariant: I'm flattered, really... But I gotta say no. It's not for me.

entries.femaleVariant: Understood.
We had a little fun today. Drank together.
But I see you on the street later, it won't make no difference. You're either with us, or against us.
I'll keep that in mind.
I told y'all not to trust that little shit!
Having yourselves a competition? I want in.
I'm going.
Enjoy your little circle jerk. I'm outta here.
Heh. Don't let us stop ya.
Got some kinda competition goin' on?
Yup. Lead-spittin' kind.
What? You scared I'd leave you all in the dust?
I want in.
Shit outta luck. We were about to call it.
Do you know who you're fucking talking to? Hm? I been deployed three times! Three! I fought on the front lines!
Easy, Walker. What did I say, huh? We're just here to have a good time. You got somethin' to prove, be our guest. Heh, it'll be fun.
Well, come on! Drink!
Who you tryin' to impress, girl? You don't got the skills, fine. No need to make a damn fool of yourself, too.
entries.maleVariant: Who you tryin' to impress, choom? You don't got the skills, fine. No need to make a damn fool of yourself, too.

entries.femaleVariant: No no no, just don't go past the line when shooting. Automatic disqualification.
Over the line! Disqualified!
You cross that line and shoot, you're outta the game!
Well, bravo, champ! Fun's over for you.
'Ey, toe that line. We don't like cheaters here.
Hey hey, hold it! What, you thought I wouldn't notice?
Don't forget the line! One toe over and you're gone!
That's it, you're out! In the home stretch, too!
